features: 【30KPa Powerful Suction & Whole House Cleaning】ORFELD cordless vacuum cleaner is equipped with the latest brushless motor, which can provide 30000Pa strong suction in MAX mode, which can capture crumbs, dust, crumbs, pet hair and other debris instantly and easily. Two suction modes are optional, and the standard mode can run for up to 50 minutes, which is enough to clean the whole house.

【Multifunctional Vacuum & 2-in-1 Rolling Brush】This hardwood floor vacuum is equipped with multifunctional accessories, including dusting brush and long crevice tool, which can be easily converted into a handheld vacuum cleaner to meet all your daily cleaning needs. The 2-in-1 roller brush can directly clean various surfaces such as carpets and hardwood floors, eliminating the trouble of frequent replacement of roller brushes.

【5-stage High Efficiency Filtration System】Cordless stick vacuum cleaner adopts a new 5-stage fully sealed cyclone filtration system with double HEPA filters, effectively capturing 99.99% of dust particles as small as 0.3 microns to avoid secondary pollution and provide clean air for your family. The package is equipped with 2 replaceable HEPA filters, regular cleaning of the filters prevents insufficient suction power and clogging.

【Flexible Electric Floor Brush & LED Headlight】The flexible electric floor brush head of the rechargeable cordless vacuum cleaner has flexible 180° sideways rotation and 90° up and down rotation, allowing you to clean your home in all directions without moving furniture. 5 LED headlights to clean dark areas under furniture and beds without missing any hidden dust.

【Humanized Design Vacuum Cleaner】The main body weight of the household lightweight vacuum cleaner is only 4.6 lbs and the ergonomic handle design will not make your hands feel tired even if you use it for a long time. Triple noise reduction technology makes the hard floor vacuum less than 63db. Wall-mounted storage design for easy storage and space-saving.
【Worry-free After-sales】No need to worry about after-sales problems, the ORFELD vacuum cleaner provides 24*7 all-weather support and 24-month warranty.

reviews.reviewText: We bought this to replace a dirt devil that had been weak and almost useless since we purchased it. The battery lasts a good while. I've never run it down in less than 5 uses. The suction strength is also impressive for a handheld vacuum. This is a great little vacuum. It does a great job sucking up stink bugs as they cling to leaves and straw and I can only imagine how great it would be at cleaning up stuff that doesn’t resist being sucked into it. Definitely a great purchase!

Ich bin absolut begeistert vom ORFELD Akku Staubsauger! Dieser kabellose Handstaubsauger hat sich als äußerst leistungsstark und praktisch erwiesen.Mit nur 2,6 Pfund ist der Staubsauger leicht und einfach zu handhaben. Der leistungsstarke Akku ermöglicht eine beeindruckende Saugkraft, die problemlos mit herkömmlichen kabelgebundenen Staubsaugern mithalten kann. Die kabellose Funktionalität bietet eine unglaubliche Bewegungsfreiheit, sodass das Staubsaugen mühelos und effizient vonstattengeht.Die verschiedenen Aufsätze und Düsen machen den ORFELD Staubsauger äußerst vielseitig. Egal ob auf Hartböden oder Teppichen, er liefert hervorragende Ergebnisse. Die Handhabung ist intuitiv und das leichte Gewicht macht ihn besonders benutzerfreundlich.Der Akku hält erstaunlich lange, was die Effizienz des Staubsaugens weiter steigert. Die einfache Entleerung des Staubbehälters und die pflegeleichte Reinigung tragen zusätzlich zur positiven Erfahrung bei.Insgesamt kann ich den ORFELD Akku Staubsauger wärmstens empfehlen. Er vereint Leistung, Handlichkeit und eine lange Akkulaufzeit in einem kompakten Design. Dieser Staubsauger hat meine Erwartungen übertroffen und erleichtert die Hausarbeit erheblich!

reviews.reviewTitle: [Aspirapolvere cordless Orfeld EV-678] Compatto, leggero e potente
reviews.reviewText: Mi serviva un piccolo aspirapolvere da tenere in garage e non volevo spendere molto. Ho scelto questo per prezzo e dimensioni, credendo di prendere qualcosa che potesse aspirare solo la polvere.Mi sono dovuto ricredere. Innanzitutto la dotazione di accessori è molto ricca. Ci sono 2 filtri lavabili, ben 4 beccucci ed il caricabatteria con supporto per appenderlo al muro (tasselli e viti incluse). Quest'ultimo è tutt'altro che scontato, anche su fasce di prezzo leggermente superiori.Esteticamente è molto gradevole, ma sopratutto è molto compatto e leggero (meno di 1 Kg).Ottimo il potere di aspirazione e, devo dire, meno rumoroso di altri aspirapolvere simili che ho.La batteria si ricarica semplicemente mettendo l'aspirapolvere sulla basetta, sulla quale è possibile lasciarlo per tutto il tempo che non lo si utilizza.La capacità di 2.2 Ah permette un utilizzo continuativo di quasi mezz'ora, anche più di quello che mi serviva.Spero che duri nel tempo (fortunatamente c'è sempre l'ottima assistenza Amazon, in aggiunta a quella del produttore)
La he estado usando con mucha frecuencia y la verdad es que va genial, para el coche va muy bien por su potencia y versatilidad, además que con los accesorios te permite sacarle más provecho
